                    <span>As an aspiring opera singer, I think "Bird By Bird" speaks to any artist who is struggling with the desire to share their gift with a world that is full of rejection.  Anne's insights are fantastically sarcastic and full of truth.  Thank you for speaking my mind, Anne.  I have quoted you through tears of laughter to more than one friend.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">She held my hand, this is a masterpiece</div>
                    <div>
